[sub_resource type="Resource" id="Resource_k8cdx"]
script = ExtResource("6_cn7je")
titulo = "Fire Arms"
texto_ayuda = "[b]Fire Arms[/b] 

[table=2, center]
[cell][img=105%]res://assets/sprites/FireArmsIndicator.png[/img][/cell][cell][font_size=11]In the lower left corner, in addition to seeing the player's condition, you can see what weapon he is using and if he has ammunition.[/font_size][/cell]
[/table]
[font_size=11]The fire arms and ammunition equipment that you can find in the game are listed below:[/font_size]

[table=2]
[cell][center][img=150]res://assets/sprites/FireArms4.png[/img][/center][/cell][cell][font_size=11]To use a grenade, pull the pin while holding the lever down. Aim at your target, then throw the grenade in a quick, fluid motion. After throwing, immediately take cover to avoid the explosion.[/font_size][/cell]

[cell][center][img=75%]res://assets/sprites/FireArms1.png[/img][/center][/cell][cell][font_size=11]To use a grenade, pull the pin while holding the lever down. Aim at your target, then throw the grenade in a quick, fluid motion. After throwing, immediately take cover to avoid the explosion.[/font_size][/cell]

[cell][center][img=150]res://assets/sprites/FireArms2.png[/img][/center][/cell][cell][font_size=11]To use a rifle, hold it steady, aim through the sight or scope at a distant target, and squeeze the trigger gently to fire[/font_size][/cell]


[cell][center][img=75%]res://assets/sprites/FireArms3.png[/img][/center][/cell][cell][font_size=11]Using a pistol you must to approach the target at close range, aim quickly at the center mass, and pull the trigger with a firm grip.[/font_size][/cell]

[cell][center][img=75%]res://assets/sprites/FireArms5.png[/img][/center][/cell][cell][font_size=11]Pistol ammunition[/font_size][/cell]

[/table]
"

[sub_resource type="Resource" id="Resource_n03jy"]
script = ExtResource("6_cn7je")
titulo = "Blades"
texto_ayuda = "[b]Fire Arms[/b] 
[table=2]
[cell][center][img=75%]res://assets/sprites/Blades1.png[/img][/center][/cell][cell][font_size=11]To use a grenade, pull the pin while holding the lever down.[/font_size][/cell]


[cell][center][img=75%]res://assets/sprites/blade2.png[/img][/center][/cell][cell][font_size=11]This second type of blade, although less common, has a higher level of damage to its opponents.[/font_size][/cell]
[/table]
[font_size=11]In a game, blades can be versatile weapons used for both offense and defense. Players can use them to perform quick, light attacks that deal damage in rapid succession or execute powerful strikes with slower, more deliberate movements. Blades are often effective in close combat, allowing players to dodge or parry incoming attacks while staying mobile[/font_size]

[font_size=11]To make the most of blades, focus on speed and precision. Timing your attacks and dodges is key to outmaneuvering enemies. Some games may also let you upgrade blades with special abilities, like increasing damage, adding elemental effects, or enhancing critical hit chances[/font_size]


"

